  "excerpt": "<p>The Data Migration Object scorecard is designed to keep track of your Salesforce data migration project and can serve as a launchpad to link to supporting data assets </p>",
  "content_html": "\n<div class=\"wp-block-genesis-blocks-gb-container gb-block-container\"><div class=\"gb-container-inside\"><div class=\"gb-container-content\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-genesis-blocks-gb-columns gb-layout-columns-1 one-column\"><div class=\"gb-layout-column-wrap gb-block-layout-column-gap-2 gb-is-responsive-column\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-genesis-blocks-gb-column gb-block-layout-column\"><div class=\"gb-block-layout-column-inner\">\n<p>The Data Migration Scorecard is designed to keep track of your Salesforce data migration project and can serve as a launchpad to link to supporting data assets including but not limited to:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>ETL jobs</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Data Pipeline Services</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Documentation </li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>When linking to an external resource the Status is transformed into a clickable URL .</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/image-5-1024x576.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-8760\" srcset=\"https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/image-5-1024x576.png 1024w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/image-5-300x169.png 300w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/image-5-768x432.png 768w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/image-5-1536x865.png 1536w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/image-5-2048x1153.png 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Update Status and Link to an External URL:</h2>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Once you have <a href=\"https://datatoolspro.com/tutorials/salesforce-migration-field-mapping-details/#addsourceobjects\" title=\"\">added your source object</a>, click the &#8220;Edit&#8221; icon on the right denoted by a pencil icon.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>In the edit record screen, you can update the status and add URLs to any external resource.</li>\n</ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"741\" src=\"https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/image-15-1024x741.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-8771\" style=\"width:439px;height:317px\" srcset=\"https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/image-15-1024x741.png 1024w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/image-15-300x217.png 300w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/image-15-768x556.png 768w, https://datatoolspro.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/image-15.png 1518w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>PRO TIP:</strong> To ensure nothing is missed, we recommend mining your source database to fetch all distinct values that could be migrated and entering them into the data mapping tool.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Additional Tutorials: Data Mapping &amp; Migration</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-genesis-blocks-gb-columns gb-layout-columns-3 gb-3-col-equal\"><div class=\"gb-layout-column-wrap gb-block-layout-column-gap-2 gb-is-responsive-column\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-genesis-blocks-gb-column gb-block-layout-column\"><div class=\"gb-block-layout-column-inner\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-datatools-pro wp-block-embed-datatools-pro\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<div class=\"ratio ratio-16x9\"><blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"PaoOWd682a\"><a href=\"https://datatoolspro.com/tutorials/salesforce-migration-field-mapping-details/\">Salesforce Migration Field Mapping Details</a></blockquote><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; visibility: hidden;\" title=\"&#8220;Salesforce Migration Field Mapping Details&#8221; &#8212; DataTools Pro\" src=\"https://datatoolspro.com/tutorials/salesforce-migration-field-mapping-details/embed/#?secret=eGVz1chQb5#?secret=PaoOWd682a\" data-secret=\"PaoOWd682a\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></div>\n</div></figure>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-genesis-blocks-gb-column gb-block-layout-column\"><div class=\"gb-block-layout-column-inner\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-datatools-pro wp-block-embed-datatools-pro\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<div class=\"ratio ratio-16x9\"><blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"IDYspUMKIj\"><a href=\"https://datatoolspro.com/tutorials/mapping-and-migrating-salesforce-picklists/\">Mapping and Migrating Salesforce Picklists</a></blockquote><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; visibility: hidden;\" title=\"&#8220;Mapping and Migrating Salesforce Picklists&#8221; &#8212; DataTools Pro\" src=\"https://datatoolspro.com/tutorials/mapping-and-migrating-salesforce-picklists/embed/#?secret=pUvsESU2WU#?secret=IDYspUMKIj\" data-secret=\"IDYspUMKIj\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></div>\n</div></figure>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-genesis-blocks-gb-column gb-block-layout-column\"><div class=\"gb-block-layout-column-inner\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-datatools-pro wp-block-embed-datatools-pro\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<div class=\"ratio ratio-16x9\"><blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"yGz8r9o1i5\"><a href=\"https://datatoolspro.com/tutorials/migration-export-sql/\">Migration Export SQL</a></blockquote><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; visibility: hidden;\" title=\"&#8220;Migration Export SQL&#8221; &#8212; DataTools Pro\" src=\"https://datatoolspro.com/tutorials/migration-export-sql/embed/#?secret=dDq9zsiIZf#?secret=yGz8r9o1i5\" data-secret=\"yGz8r9o1i5\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></div>\n</div></figure>\n</div></div>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n</div></div>\n</div></div>\n</div></div></div>\n"
